OL,5, Airline passengers should take just one
OL,6, carry-on bag on holiday with them and  
OL,7, not check-in luggage to avoid delays,  
OL,8, according to industry figures.         
OL,10,FThe GMB union, which represents        
OL,11,Faviation workers, said if people don't 
OL,12,Fcheck-in luggage it "limits the        
OL,13,Fdisruption".                           
OL,15,FHundreds of flights have been cancelled
OL,16,Fthis week due to staff shortages across
OL,17,Fthe sector.                            
OL,19,FThe industry has met with the          
OL,20,Fgovernment to address the problems.    
